{"TopicId":206851,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"How to rearrange icons in the stock toolbar?","CreatedByName":"serg.bloim","CreatedById":143535,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-10T16:25:35Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"serg.bloim","CreatedById":143535,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-10T16:25:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi there. I have a couple of mods. Enough for scroll buttons to appear on my toolbar.\u003Cbr\u003E\nApparently some icons I use most of the times are in the very bottom of it. And I wish I can rearrange them, so I don\u0027t need to scroll all the time.\u003Cbr\u003E\nIs there a way or mod how to reorder these icons?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks!\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022image.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022301.82\u0022 height=\u0022498\u0022 width=\u0022165\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.ibb.co/pzyDnnL/image.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-02-10T16:35:08Z\u0022 title=\u002202/10/2022 04:35  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 10, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by serg.bloim\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003ETypos\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Snark","CreatedById":125662,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-11T15:17:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t know of any such functionality in the stock game, but I wouldn\u0027t be surprised if there\u0027s a mod for that. My suggestion would be to ask about it over in Add-on Discussions.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"fleventeen","CreatedById":220622,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-10T03:06:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can\u0027t stand the stock toolbar, but luckily we have this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022129964\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u002